import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import alansal as al
import noktasal as no
In[2]:
I = plt.imread("../data/rose.png")[:, :, :3]

# bulanklatrma evriim ekirdei
h = (
    np.array(
        [
            [1, 1, 1],
            [1, 1, 1],
            [1, 1, 1],
        ]
    )
    / 9
)

J = al.evrisim(I, h)

plt.imshow(J)
plt.show()

    [
        [0, -1, 0],

In[6]:
I = plt.imread("../data/rose.png")[:, :, :3]
I = no.gray_scale(I)

# kenar alglama evriim ekirdei
h = np.array(
    [
        [0, -1, 0],
        [-1, 4, -1],
        [0, -1, 0],
    ]
)

J = np.clip(al.evrisim(I, h) + 0.5, 0, 1)

plt.imshow(J)
plt.show()
